# AI PDF Question Answering Agent (RAG)

An AI agent that answers questions from a PDF document using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

## Features

- Load PDF documents
- Convert text into embeddings
- Store vectors in FAISS database
- Retrieve relevant content
- Generate answers using LLM

## Tech Stack

- Python
- LangChain
- OpenAI Embeddings
- FAISS Vector Database

## Installation

Clone the repository and install dependencies:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-pdf-rag.git
cd ai-pdf-rag
pip install -r requirements.txt
